Class AliasService

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.sakaiproject.alias.cover.AliasService
  • Deprecated. 
    Static covers should not be used in favour of injection or lookup via the component manager. This cover will be removed in a later version of the Kernel

    public class AliasService
extends Object

    AliasService is a static Cover for the AliasService; see that interface for usage details.
